    <description>The CCD imager features a Tektronik 2kx2k chip with 24-micron pixels and has a digital limitation of 65,534, a bias level of approximately 1000, and a noise of 4.0 e-/RMS. The default gain is 3.6 e/A, with linearity around 180,000 e- at 0.1% and 190,000 e- at 1.0%. It shows an internal radiation event rate of roughly 2700 events/hr and a dark current of 4-5 e-/hr/pix. Mounted on a 2.1m telescope at f/7.5, it offers a field of view of 10.4' x 10.4' and a pixel scale of 0.305'/pix.</description>
